{{main|FINA Synchronised Swimming World Trophy}}

The '''2nd [[FINA]] Synchronised Swimming World Trophy''' was held 2007 in [[Rio de Janeiro, Brazil]]. It featured swimmers from 8 nations, swimming in three events: Duet, Team and Free Combination.<ref>[http://www.fina.org/project/docs/histoFina/HistoFINA_IX.pdf HistoFINA, volume 9] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924051803/http://www.fina.org/project/docs/histoFina/HistoFINA_IX.pdf |date=2015-09-24 }} published by [[FINA]] on 2009-07-01; retrieved 2013-08-09.</ref>

