'''Košarkaški klub Žarkovo''' ({{lang-sr-cyrl|Кошаркашки клуб Жарково}}), commonly referred to as '''KK Žarkovo''', is a men's professional [[basketball]] [[Sports club|club]] based in [[Belgrade]], [[Serbia]]. They are currently competing in the [[Basketball League of Serbia B|Second League of Serbia]]. 

The club was founded in 1975 and was named after [[Žarkovo]], an [[List of Belgrade neighborhoods|urban neighborhood]] of Belgrade.

